Steps to build the project.

1) Install and configure CUDA;
	http://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/cuda-installation-guide-linux/index.html#axzz4ozmEKlUs

2) Install and configure OpenCV;
	http://docs.opencv.org/2.4/doc/tutorials/introduction/linux_install/linux_install.html

3) On the terminal, go to the build/ directory and type 
	
	$ cmake ..

4) Compile the source code for the project by executing

	$ make


